{"tid":1830293,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"回望過去7個月 我地嘅年輕人日行30公里 和理非1118槍林彈雨衝彌敦道","createTime":"2020-01-19T13:05:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-20T03:29:20.000Z","uid":123774,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d1ccf9fb036be1b0ee6fd30a4d5aa1a364413bd4","tid":1830293,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T13:05:58.000Z","msg":"我覺得做左好多創舉<br />\n<br />\n從來未諗過10幾歲細路咁好體力<br />\n東涌行入機場機場行去青衣交匯處<br />\n黎明行動連續24個鐘兩日行動<br />\n黑警都有輪更 我地班細路唔知點捱大 可以打足一日<br />\n<br />\n講大人 好多係和理非<br />\n但救理大 成條彌敦道滿晒人<br />\n槍林彈雨班和理非照衝唔退後<br />\n<br />\n仲有好多例子<br />\n林病和你傾我地嘅市民每個有備而來<br />\n細微到而家電視台隨便響街度搵一個示威者訪問<br />\n佢哋都好ready知道自己想講乜message<br />\n<br />\n呢7個月 大家都進化左"},{"pid":"d829ff90546d85b84250375cfde10554635a58d8","tid":1830293,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T13:06:59.000Z","msg":"【攬炒新年】[行動PO]  對準政權！ 喚醒港豬！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1830245\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1830245</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f14a82455cdf12edddc8d95f62bc210dfebf8817","tid":1830293,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T13:07:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"116c7b68fff2468c301f4415ffe173a8359c855b","tid":1830293,"uid":188907,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T13:10:02.000Z","msg":"有血有淚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無論最後贏定輸<br />\n我呢世人最光榮ge事就係可以同各位手足共同進退"},{"pid":"745310b9ab16833cf2274cf43ca4ffa23545f666","tid":1830293,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T13:15:33.000Z","msg":"不能忘"},{"pid":"946c44d1ad429648b8f26849953a2d1bb107a156","tid":1830293,"uid":308567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T13:26:43.000Z","msg":"Retweet<br />\n<br />\n50秒有槍殺手無寸鐵既啊叔<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/XinqiSu/status/1218816278820835329\"